text: Egil Borgen Johansen (14 March 1934 - 5 March 1993) was a Norwegian archer. Borgen Johansen competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics.Egil Borgen JohansenEgil Borgen JOHANSEN == References == Category:1934 births Category:1993 deaths Category:Norwegian archers Category:Olympians for Norway
